data.description: Great neighborhood and school zone. (Pool) This home is truly incredible! Open concept, 2,188 sq ft, 4 bed, 3 full bath, located in a cul-de-sac on 1 acre. 42x18 in ground swimming pool with auto cover, hot tub and gazebo with drop down bar, lots of concerte around pool. Tile counter tops with backsplash. Hardwood floors in dinning, kitchen, family, and entry way. Vaulted ceilings in Kitchen, dining, formal, and master bedroom. Master bedroom has walk-in closet and offers a garden tub in master bath. Master is upstairs.Additional property info: http://www.forsalebyowner.com/listing/WS298?provider_id=28079
